10 An Act relating to confidential records; prescribing
right of victims to confidentiality of certain crime
11 scene and autopsy photographs; requiring certain
photographs submitted to the Pardon and Parole Board
12 be kept confidential; amending 51 O.S. 2021, Section
24A.5, as last amended by Section 2, Chapter 116,
13 O.S.L. 2024 (51 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 24A.5),
which relates to the Open Records Act; adding certain
14 victim photographs to list of confidential records;
prohibiting certain victim photographs submitted to
15 the Board from being presented to the public;
requiring parties to submit two separate clemency
16 hearing packets to the Board; clarifying contents for
each packet; allowing Board to seal certain records;
17 clarifying which packet the Governor will receive;
providing for codification; and providing an
18 effective date.
